(a) Banking Act 1970;

(b) Finance Companies Act 1967;

(c) Financial Advisers Act 2001;

(d) Financial Holding Companies Act 2013;

(da) Financial Services and Markets Act 2022; [Act 18 of 2022 wef 28/04/2023]

(e) Insurance Act 1966;

